---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Covenant-Class Colony Ships"
  description="CY78.3 Affiance-class extended range colony vessel. 1,200 meters, solar sail array, 2,000 colonists, WALTER AI system. The pinnacle of colony ship engineering. Carrying humanity to new horizons."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden scanlines border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center pt-20 pb-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          COLONY SHIPS -- VESSEL CLASS PROFILE
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-[9rem] font-black text-white mb-4 leading-none uppercase">
          COVENANT<br/><span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">CLASS</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-48 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-6"></div>

        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          CY78.3 AFFIANCE-CLASS EXTENDED RANGE COLONY VESSEL
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Vessel Data Bar -->
    <section class="relative bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 divide-x divide-[#1a1a1a]">
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">CLASS</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">CY78.3 AFFIANCE</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">LENGTH</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">1,200 METERS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">COLONIST CAPACITY</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">2,000</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">AI SYSTEM</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600]">WALTER</div>
          </div>
          <div class="py-8 px-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">STATUS</div>
            <div class="text-sm font-black text-[#FFC600] status-active">IN SERVICE</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overview -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
            <div>
              <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
                CLASS OVERVIEW
              </div>
              <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-8">
                CARRYING HUMANITY'S <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">FUTURE</span> TO NEW HORIZONS
              </h2>
              <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE COVENANT-CLASS COLONY SHIP REPRESENTS THE ABSOLUTE PINNACLE OF INTERSTELLAR VESSEL ENGINEERING. DESIGNATED CY78.3 AFFIANCE-CLASS, THESE EXTENDED-RANGE COLONY VESSELS ARE PURPOSE-BUILT FOR DECADE-LONG VOYAGES TO FRONTIER WORLDS, CARRYING EVERYTHING NEEDED TO ESTABLISH A NEW COLONY FROM THE GROUND UP.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> AT 1,200 METERS IN LENGTH, THE COVENANT-CLASS IS AMONG THE LARGEST VESSELS EVER CONSTRUCTED. ITS MASSIVE SOLAR SAIL ARRAY SUPPLEMENTS ONBOARD POWER GENERATION DURING INTERSTELLAR TRANSIT, WHILE AN INTEGRATED TERRAFORMING MODULE WITH AUTOMATED ATMOSPHERE PROCESSOR ENSURES THE VESSEL ARRIVES AT ITS DESTINATION READY TO BEGIN WORLD-BUILDING OPERATIONS IMMEDIATELY.
                </p>
                <p>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-black">&gt;</span> THE COVENANT-CLASS CARRIES UP TO 2,000 COLONISTS IN HYPERSLEEP, SUPPORTED BY AN EMBRYO NURSERY WITH 1,400 HUMAN EMBRYOS TO ACCELERATE POPULATION GROWTH POST-LANDING. A CREW OF 15 MANAGES SHIPBOARD OPERATIONS, ASSISTED BY THE WALTER INTEGRATED AI SYSTEM -- THE MOST ADVANCED SYNTHETIC INTELLIGENCE PLATFORM EVER DEPLOYED ON A SPACECRAFT.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="corp-card p-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-6 uppercase border-b-2 border-[#FFC600] pb-3">TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS</h3>
              <div class="space-y-4 text-sm font-mono">
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">DESIGNATION</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">COVENANT-CLASS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">MODEL</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">CY78.3 AFFIANCE</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">TYPE</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">EXT. RANGE COLONY VESSEL</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">LENGTH</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">1,200 METERS</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">COLONISTS</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">2,000 (HYPERSLEEP)</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">EMBRYO CAPACITY</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">1,400</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">CREW</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">15</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">AI SYSTEM</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">WALTER</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-3">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">POWER</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">SOLAR SAIL + REACTOR</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-between">
                  <span class="text-gray-500 uppercase">TERRAFORMING</span>
                  <span class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold">INTEGRATED MODULE</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Features -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black border-t-4 border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 pt-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
            FEATURES
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-4">
            KEY <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">SYSTEMS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">WA</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">WALTER AI SYSTEM</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              THE MOST ADVANCED SYNTHETIC INTELLIGENCE PLATFORM EVER DEPLOYED. WALTER MANAGES ALL AUTONOMOUS NAVIGATION, SYSTEMS MONITORING, COLONIST LIFE SUPPORT, AND EMERGENCY RESPONSE. CAPABLE OF INDEPENDENT DECISION-MAKING ACROSS ALL SHIPBOARD OPERATIONS FOR THE DURATION OF MULTI-YEAR VOYAGES.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">SS</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">SOLAR SAIL ARRAY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              A MASSIVE DEPLOYABLE SOLAR SAIL ARRAY HARVESTS STELLAR RADIATION DURING TRANSIT TO SUPPLEMENT ONBOARD POWER GENERATION. THE ARRAY REDUCES REACTOR FUEL CONSUMPTION BY UP TO 40% ON STANDARD ROUTES, EXTENDING THE VESSEL'S OPERATIONAL RANGE TO THE FARTHEST REACHES OF EXPLORED SPACE.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">TF</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">TERRAFORMING MODULE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              AN INTEGRATED TERRAFORMING MODULE WITH AUTOMATED ATMOSPHERE PROCESSOR ALLOWS THE COVENANT-CLASS TO BEGIN ATMOSPHERIC CONVERSION UPON ARRIVAL AT ITS DESTINATION. THE MODULE IS DESIGNED FOR SURFACE DEPLOYMENT AND CAN OPERATE INDEPENDENTLY ONCE INSTALLED.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">HC</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">HYPERSLEEP COMPLEX</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              2,000 INDIVIDUAL HYPERSLEEP PODS ARRANGED IN CLIMATE-CONTROLLED BAYS. EACH POD IS INDEPENDENTLY MONITORED BY THE WALTER SYSTEM WITH REDUNDANT LIFE SUPPORT AND EMERGENCY REVIVAL CAPABILITY. DESIGNED FOR UNINTERRUPTED SUSPENSION PERIODS EXCEEDING TEN YEARS.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">EN</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">EMBRYO NURSERY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              A DEDICATED CRYOGENIC EMBRYO STORAGE FACILITY HOUSING 1,400 HUMAN EMBRYOS. THE NURSERY ENSURES ACCELERATED POPULATION GROWTH AT THE DESTINATION, PROVIDING THE DEMOGRAPHIC FOUNDATION FOR A SELF-SUSTAINING COLONY WITHIN A SINGLE GENERATION OF ARRIVAL.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#FFC600] clip-corner flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-black font-black text-lg">AN</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-3 uppercase">AUTONOMOUS NAVIGATION</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">
              FULLY AUTONOMOUS NAVIGATION CAPABILITY ALLOWS THE COVENANT-CLASS TO TRANSIT BETWEEN STAR SYSTEMS WITHOUT CREW INTERVENTION. THE WALTER SYSTEM CONTINUOUSLY MONITORS COURSE, ADJUSTS FOR NAVIGATIONAL HAZARDS, AND OPTIMIZES FUEL EFFICIENCY THROUGHOUT THE VOYAGE.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Profile -->
    <section class="relative py-28 bg-black">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 clip-corner">
              MISSION
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white mb-4">
              MISSION <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">PROFILE</span>
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">VOYAGE DURATION</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">DESIGNED FOR VOYAGES RANGING FROM 2 TO 15 YEARS DEPENDING ON DESTINATION. ALL COLONISTS AND NON-ESSENTIAL CREW REMAIN IN HYPERSLEEP FOR THE DURATION. WALTER AND A ROTATING SKELETON CREW MAINTAIN WATCH.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">ARRIVAL PROTOCOL</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">UPON ARRIVAL, THE COVENANT-CLASS ENTERS ORBIT AND BEGINS SYSTEMATIC SURFACE SURVEY. CREW ARE REVIVED FIRST, FOLLOWED BY STAGED COLONIST REVIVAL. TERRAFORMING MODULE IS DEPLOYED TO SURFACE WITHIN THE FIRST 72 HOURS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">COLONY ESTABLISHMENT</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">THE VESSEL CARRIES ALL MATERIALS AND EQUIPMENT NECESSARY TO ESTABLISH INITIAL COLONY INFRASTRUCTURE: HABITAT MODULES, POWER GENERATORS, AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS, MEDICAL FACILITIES, AND COMMUNICATIONS EQUIPMENT.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 border-2 border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner hover:border-[#FFC600] transition-colors">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-black text-white uppercase mb-4">VESSEL RETIREMENT</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs leading-relaxed">ONCE A COLONY IS ESTABLISHED, THE COVENANT-CLASS VESSEL IS TYPICALLY DECOMMISSIONED IN ORBIT AND ITS COMPONENTS REPURPOSED AS ORBITAL INFRASTRUCTURE, COMMUNICATION RELAY, OR EMERGENCY SHELTER.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="terminal mt-16">
            <div class="terminal-content">
              <p class="text-[#FFC600] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
                &gt; "WHEN A COVENANT-CLASS VESSEL DEPARTS LUNA ORBIT, IT CARRIES MORE THAN COLONISTS AND CARGO. IT CARRIES THE ENTIRE FUTURE OF A WORLD. EVERYTHING NEEDED TO TRANSFORM A BARREN PLANET INTO A HOME FOR HUMANITY IS ABOARD THAT SHIP. THE COVENANT-CLASS IS NOT JUST AN ENGINEERING ACHIEVEMENT. IT IS A DECLARATION THAT HUMANITY WILL ENDURE AMONG THE STARS."
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <section class="relative py-12 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/fleet" class="btn-secondary">ALL FLEET</a>
          <a href="/fleet/nostromo-class" class="btn-secondary">NOSTROMO-CLASS</a>
          <a href="/fleet/conestoga-class" class="btn-secondary">CONESTOGA-CLASS</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
